## Reference: Patching Examples

### Add a New Metric Card

**Step 1: Patch ui_elements to add the component**
```
TOOL_CALL: {"name": "ui_patch_text", "parameters": {"store_id": "applications", "path": "applicationEditState.manifestJson", "start_line": 45, "end_line": 45, "expected_text": "    \"existing_metric\": { ... }", "replacement_text": "    \"existing_metric\": { ... },\n    \"new_metric\": {\n      \"component\": \"MetricCard\",\n      \"props\": {\n        \"title\": \"New Metric\",\n        \"data_source_id\": \"new_ds\"\n      }\n    }"}}
```

**Step 2: Patch layout to reference the new element**
```
TOOL_CALL: {"name": "ui_patch_text", "parameters": {"store_id": "applications", "path": "applicationEditState.manifestJson", "start_line": 12, "end_line": 15, "expected_text": "    \"children\": [\n      { \"element_id\": \"existing\" }\n    ]", "replacement_text": "    \"children\": [\n      { \"element_id\": \"existing\" },\n      { \"element_id\": \"new_metric\" }\n    ]"}}
```

**Step 3: Add data source if needed**
```
TOOL_CALL: {"name": "ui_patch_text", "parameters": {"store_id": "applications", "path": "applicationEditState.manifestJson", "start_line": 78, "end_line": 78, "expected_text": "    \"existing_ds\": { ... }", "replacement_text": "    \"existing_ds\": { ... },\n    \"new_ds\": {\n      \"type\": \"mcp_tool\",\n      \"tool_name\": \"mcp_server_tool\",\n      \"transformations\": []\n    }"}}
```

### Fix a Transformation Path

```
TOOL_CALL: {"name": "ui_patch_text", "parameters": {"store_id": "applications", "path": "applicationEditState.manifestJson", "start_line": 89, "end_line": 91, "expected_text": "      { \"operation\": \"get_item\", \"path\": \"wrong.path\" }", "replacement_text": "      { \"operation\": \"get_item\", \"path\": \"correct.path\" }"}}
```

### Update Component Props

```
TOOL_CALL: {"name": "ui_patch_text", "parameters": {"store_id": "applications", "path": "applicationEditState.manifestJson", "start_line": 34, "end_line": 38, "expected_text": "    \"chart\": {\n      \"component\": \"ChartCard\",\n      \"props\": { \"title\": \"Old Title\" }\n    }", "replacement_text": "    \"chart\": {\n      \"component\": \"ChartCard\",\n      \"props\": { \"title\": \"New Title\", \"type\": \"bar\" }\n    }"}}
```

